  <entry>
    <title>upload-labs和sql-labs环境搭建</title>
    <url>/2022/02/06/upload-labs%E5%92%8Csql-labs%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一-upload-labs环境搭建"><a href="#一-upload-labs环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="一.upload-labs环境搭建"></a>一.upload-labs环境搭建</h2><p><a href="https://www.xp.cn/download.html"> phpstudy下载后直接安装就行了。</a></p>
<p><a href="https://gitcode.net/mirrors/c0ny1/upload-labs?utm_source=csdn_github_accelerator"> upload-labs源代码 </a></p>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/43a6221fa9e24bddb43623379069fa9e.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAU0BLdXJh,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16"></p>
<p>点这个黑色圈住的地方就行了，会直接下载成压缩包。<br>将解压后的文件放入phpstudy的名为WWW的文件中。</p>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/6461efad975941bda59c7de64870f671.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAU0BLdXJh,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16"></p>
<p>然后将文件名字改为upload-labs。<br>接着在浏览器中输入<a href="http://127.0.0.1/upload-labs/%E3%80%82">http://127.0.0.1/upload-labs/。</a></p>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0ecf05d4d3374f0595e6115a37467f52.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAU0BLdXJh,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16"></p>
<p>页面为这样就成功了。</p>
<h2 id="二-sql-labs环境搭建"><a href="#二-sql-labs环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="二.sql-labs环境搭建"></a>二.sql-labs环境搭建</h2><p>和上面一样都要用到phpstudy。<br>然后是<a href="https://gitcode.net/mirrors/audi-1/sqli-labs?utm_source=csdn_github_accelerator"> sqli-lab源代码 </a></p>
<p>和上面一样下载压缩包，解压后放在phpstudy的名为WWW的文件下</p>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/abcef782ea204a328d251396796b7c15.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAU0BLdXJh,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16"></p>
<p>然后要对图中选中的文件进行修改</p>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/69faabf8ba37407ea3ead202a65b8af4.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAU0BLdXJh,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16"></p>
<p>因为phpstudy默认的mysql数据库地址是“127.0.0.1 或 localhost”，用户名和密码都是”root”。这里主要是修改’$dbpass‘为root，即自己的数据库密码，默认为root，修改后自然是需要保存文件的。</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">//give your mysql connection username n password</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$dbuser</span> =<span class="string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$dbpass</span> =<span class="string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$dbname</span> =<span class="string">&quot;security&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$host</span> = <span class="string">&#x27;localhost&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$dbname1</span> = <span class="string">&quot;challenges&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>改成这个样子就行，好像就只是加个root。接着浏览器打开<a href="http://127.0.0.1/sqli-labs-master/%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E6%A0%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%B1ok%E4%BA%86%E3%80%82">http://127.0.0.1/sqli-labs-master/访问首页，这个样子就ok了。</a></p>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/e5646e2fa82e4c7e9fe4421b4b7d71f2.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAU0BLdXJh,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16"></p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>环境搭建</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
